                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "Hold. This corridor is a restricted Company transmission asset. Your presence is a fault the grid will correct, one way or another."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "The pylons carry a charter and a current. You have clearance for neither. Refuse the notice and we settle it, or step off the line and be forgotten."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "Unlicensed on a live corridor. That is a fault I am authorized to clear. Fight and clear your name, or walk off the pylon path."
                        }
                    ],
